sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Deployment and Integration
    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
    Note over User,TrustyAISvc: Flow 1 — TrustyAI Service Deployment & Integration

    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant TASCtrl as TAS Controller
    participant KServeIS as KServe InferenceService
    participant KRBP_TAS as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant TrustyAISvc as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>HTTPS/443 | Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>TASCtrl: Watch event (TrustyAIService)
    TASCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, Route<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    TASCtrl->>K8sAPI: Patch InferenceService (add inference logger)<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>KServeIS: InferenceService patched
    KServeIS->>TrustyAISvc: Inference logs<br/>HTTP/80 | None
    User->>KRBP_TAS: API request<br/>HTTPS/8443 | Bearer Token
    KRBP_TAS->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP_TAS: Authorized
    KRBP_TAS->>TrustyAISvc: Proxied request<br/>HTTP/8080 | localhost
    TrustyAISvc-->>KRBP_TAS: Response
    KRBP_TAS-->>User: HTTPS Response
    end

    %% Flow 2: LMEvalJob Execution
    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
    Note over User,OCI: Flow 2 — LMEvalJob Execution

    participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller
    participant InitC as Init Container<br/>(ta-lmes-driver)
    participant MainC as Main Container<br/>(ta-lmes-job)
    participant LMEndpoint as LM Endpoint<br/>(base_url)
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443 | Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>LMESCtrl: Watch event (LMEvalJob)
    LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod (init + main containers)<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    Note over InitC,MainC: Init container copies driver binary<br/>to shared emptyDir volume
    InitC->>InitC: Copy binary to /opt/app-root/bin/driver
    MainC->>LMEndpoint: Evaluation requests<br/>HTTP(S)/varies | Bearer Token
    LMEndpoint-->>MainC: Model responses
    LMESCtrl->>MainC: pods/exec (--get-status)<br/>SPDY | SA Token
    MainC-->>LMESCtrl: Status update (JSON)
    MainC->>OCI: Upload results (optional)<br/>HTTPS/443 | Username/Password
    LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update LMEvalJob status<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    end

    %% Flow 3: GORCH Auto-Configuration
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
    Note over User,DetectorIS: Flow 3 — Guardrails Orchestrator Auto-Configuration

    participant GORCHCtrl as GORCH Controller
    participant KRBP_GORCH as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP
    participant GeneratorIS as Generator<br/>InferenceService
    participant DetectorIS as Detector<br/>InferenceServices

    User->>K8sAPI: Create GuardrailsOrchestrator CR<br/>HTTPS/443 | Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>GORCHCtrl: Watch event (GuardrailsOrchestrator)
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: List InferenceServices<br/>(label: trustyai/guardrails=true)<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Read ServingRuntimes<br/>(detect gRPC vs REST)<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create orchestrator ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment + Routes<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    User->>KRBP_GORCH: Inference request<br/>HTTPS/8443 | Bearer Token
    KRBP_GORCH->>Orchestrator: Proxied request<br/>HTTP/8033 | localhost
    Orchestrator->>GeneratorIS: Forward to generator<br/>gRPC/HTTP | TLS / mTLS
    GeneratorIS-->>Orchestrator: Generated response
    Orchestrator->>DetectorIS: Check with detectors<br/>gRPC/HTTP | TLS / mTLS
    DetectorIS-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator-->>KRBP_GORCH: Guarded response
    KRBP_GORCH-->>User: HTTPS Response
    end
